3 (b) The limitation period in subsection (2) does not run during a time period when the individual is
4 subject to threats, intimidation, manipulation, fraudulent concealment, or fraud perpetrated by the health care
5 professional or physician who provided the medical treatment described in subsection (1) or by any person
